2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一黎太熟，二黎well done條邊太厚<br />\n<br />\n可能係<br />\n<br />\n太大火<br />\n聽人講只反一次先最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我雪櫃拎出黎室溫解涷一粒鐘到<br />\n大火起鑊兩分鐘<br />\n兩面煎一分鍾<br />\n邊位煎三十秒<br />\n最後再細火煎兩面分半鐘<br />\n<br />\n有邊d steps可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放入個學生妹個閪度過一過閪水再拿出黎食就perfect!"},{"pid":"2dbb5f3b74dd480ff1a209f6b5b413c042dc6dbf","tid":312121,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"Po上twitter tag Gordon Ramsay啦"},{"pid":"5431650d8e1c58cef31b09a95d668daa1e77e72b","tid":312121,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"你食全熟？"},{"pid":"c304802c8f8f80361939d7d47a6be3a11acae1c4","tid":312121,"uid":98860,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j7nmf94v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj7nmf94v&h=c21b74eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次整得幾好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRosemary ,sea salt ,ground black pepper ,shallot,Maitre d'Hotel butter, garlic,  unsalted butter, oregano(little),mined thyme(little), cumin(very little)<br />\n<br />\n可以交流下煎扒心得。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Lucas_delight\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLucas_delight&d=siqnVibP2mHqYsFzR%2FVzRsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=74dd99b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Lucas_delight</a>"},{"pid":"b0c2208d0ffe52bc3c97ca4b42c5a9a325eb26b2","tid":312121,"uid":18977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"Get the fuck out Outttt!"},{"pid":"a28b1c69fed36207a8032bd1c644279fdd85d67b","tid":312121,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Get the fuck out O