r />\n自己買　（大埔墟街市梁九記）<br />\n然後自己屋企焗爐焗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b944a26b350202e55e5555f465c1ea6ce3d750","tid":312121,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3038234852f2cd71193a89a7ce86cf36ec32961d","tid":312121,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:48:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebf7c3f00175af7b051ee7317dfd8342629ade34","tid":312121,"uid":93811,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:50:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一黎太熟，二黎well done條邊太厚<br />\n<br />\n可能係<br />\n<br />\n太大火<br />\n聽人講只反一次先最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我雪櫃拎出黎室溫解涷一粒鐘到<br />\n大火起鑊兩分鐘<br />\n兩面煎一分鍾<br />\n邊位煎三十秒<br />\n最後再細火煎兩面分半鐘<br />\n<br />\n有邊d steps可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n煎太耐 解凍吾夠 可以既放雪樻下格擺返一兩日做熟成 煎完rest返陣 樓主你個塊要斜切先放得入口"},{"pid":"e9a30b63a08d152af54ed5741f9e821a446a1003","tid":312121,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:56:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冰鮮肉仲食7成？<br />\n<br />\n狗都唔屌</blockquote><br />\n閣下食新鮮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當日早上劏我覺得冇咩問題<br />\n<br />\n但冰鮮得起碼幾日<br />\n<br />\n一定要全熟<br />\n<br />\n同埋冰鮮得好食極有限</blockquote><br />\n隻牛死左超過一個鐘我已經唔會食。"},{"pid":"6c61052586a8acb3c2c5e96c09458e7f5ac1ff7b","tid":312121,"uid":73848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:11:53.000Z","msg":"平時捉住隻牛咬"},{"pid":"862d4ceb41442fbce76a5bdd35f46e0bfb3c4b56","tid":312121,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冰鮮肉仲食7成？<br />\n<br />\n狗都唔屌</blockquote><br />\n閣下食新鮮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當日早上劏我覺得冇咩問題<br />\n<br />\n但冰鮮得起碼幾日<br />\n<br />\n一定要全熟<br />\n<br />\n同埋冰鮮得好食極有限</blockquote><br />\n隻牛死左超過一個鐘我已經唔會食。</blockquote><br />\n冇錯，通常係即切即食。<br />\n而且Blue Rare都嫌太熟，應該係要Raw先可以入口"},{"pid":"bb7becf590e41794c8e1d5ffcb8c9af9e69568de","tid":312121,"uid":11331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實牛排衣家野，同海鮮一樣，靚既唔洗搞甘多調味，鹽同黑白椒就ok，最多加D Rosemary番茜，甚至係超市買支Season $4X~6X一支就搞掂，只有肉質差既先要搞花臣，所以甘樣不如慳D錢去Citysuper或者其他出口店買勁靚牛排返屋企整仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n幾驚睇唔到"},{"pid":"55734c44facf52fa9debed32a6999f5b4af93936","tid":312121,"uid":125122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:50:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講 overcook 果啲真係戇鳩仔<br />\n中間仲有粉紅色，點可能係 well done?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有啲靚既牛well done 中間都係粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且對好多人黎講，過5成都係overcook"},{"pid":"63ccf1206f5b9c5de3bfca5907adabc46c5a65df","tid":312121,"uid":31266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T15:51:01.000Z","msg":"掂呀 我鍾意<br />\n因為我係例外人<br />\n唔鍾意血淋淋好多血水個種生熟度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣好似好正咁"},{"pid":"11a9741aafcf32ac5f0176ef20d13cb5e46b5e41","tid":312121,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd4b9e0cbbd5bc0c20dc9153c6bd02fbc4583d80","tid":312121,"uid":51250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冰鮮肉仲食7成？<br />\n<br />\n狗都唔屌</blockquote><br />\n閣下食新鮮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當日早上劏我覺得冇咩問題<br />\n<br />\n但冰鮮得起碼幾日<br />\n<br />\n一定要全熟<br />\n<br />\n同埋冰鮮得好食極有限</blockquote><br />\n隻牛死左超過一個鐘我已經唔會食。</blockquote><br />\n傻閪 平時係豬肉鋪買果d咪叫新鮮囉<br />\n<br />\n朝早劏完 就算放到夜晚先煮都好好味<br />\n<br />\n但一放落冰箱已經差好遠<br />\n<br />\n無論口感味道都好大分別</blockquote><br />\n你去香港啲最貴既扒房食下，問下啲牛係咪朝早劏囉，弱撚智"},{"pid":"daaab7bb87273013ebaa69b87e2aee4b0b1ead55","tid":312121,"uid":11428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:33:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一黎太熟，二黎well done條邊太厚<br />\n<br />\n可能係<br />\n<br />\n太大火<br />\n聽人講只反一次先最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我雪櫃拎出黎室溫解涷一粒鐘到<br />\n大火起鑊兩分鐘<br />\n兩面煎一分鍾<br />\n邊位煎三十秒<br />\n最後再細火煎兩面分半鐘<br />\n<br />\n有邊d steps可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n7成唔係問題，但你well done 部份太厚，起晒渣，鞋過沙紙<br />\n最好買d厚野，1.5吋，再厚就要焗先靚<br />\n<br />\n下次試下大火半分鐘一面封面，之後細返d火（其實都仲係中大火）再煎，每一分鐘反一次，煎到去心目中想要度數<br />\n<br />\n塊野離左火，d熱仲係傳緊入個心，離左火個心起碼仲可以升多3度，如果你用溫度計，早幾度好離火，佢會繼續煮同收返d汁，唔好睇少果幾度，已經夠medium 變成medium well<br />\n<br />\n幾成熟係講個溫度，你要諗下點樣煎可以令到成舊野，由面到心都差唔多溫度，你太大火/好耐先反一次，表面會太高溫熟晒，但d熱又未傳到入心，到個心有7成熟時，well done 部分就會太厚"},{"pid":"3d617466056206136cabf3dea929f3f1c2a094d0","tid":312121,"uid":11428,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/004303_29487734b8f2114561a13d7da2938ada.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F004303_29487734b8f2114561a13d7da2938ada.jpg&h=db89d828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾成熟真係好個人，靚牛不妨生d, 試下medium rare, 試過返唔到轉頭，熟晒起晒渣....我不如食其他"},{"pid":"c66de807493d6dbabced6f4e9ef23f1bb5ae3318","tid":312121,"uid":14275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>It's well done <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGood job呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWell done 係全熟喎<br />\n無啦啦good 乜job<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2faeae80813a7be091c49fb6125d0a857ff33f02","tid":312121,"uid":437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上連登問，你傻左個腦<br />\n其實好睇自己鐘意幾熟<br />\n我就食開有少少粉紅就夠，少少</blockquote><br />\n其實我追求七成熟<br />\n不過唔知呢塊係咪去到七成所以上黎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n七成太熟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a723a221bf8c51059364682a3cc2d2ca5256ca3","tid":312121,"uid":21292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"上面d 巴打講到舊肉本身既質素，可唔可以share 下係邊頭買？"},{"pid":"600b2abf06189c33879ee46ea14dbf9158cb9ca5","tid":312121,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/004303_29487734b8f2114561a13d7da2938ada.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F004303_29487734b8f2114561a13d7da2938ada.jpg&h=db89d828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾成熟真係好個人，靚牛不妨生d, 試下medium rare, 試過返唔到轉頭，熟晒起晒渣....我不如食其他</blockquote><br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾靚既牛都好<br />\n八成以上都有d哂<br />\n樓主果隻己經八成"},{"pid":"4da13e1d30a460ecf329a0a4bc694b69783fc611","tid":312121,"uid":878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:27:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ITS FUCKING OVERCOOKED!! ITS HARDER THAN A TEN YEARS OLD SLIPPER YOU DONKEY!!!!</span>"},{"pid":"e40ad08dc05703862681a0b1c09057b9714ce1ed","tid":312121,"uid":878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要 係牛扒最好買 冰鮮既<br />\n急涷硬左就冇咁有肉味<br />\n<br />\n其次要放係室溫 到room temp<br />\n最後 一定要用鑄鐵既煎ban<br />\n最後rest 5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n最重點 牛扒急涷 差好遠</blockquote><br />\n吓唔好衝出黎柒啦<br />\n靚嘅 急凍過程做得好 係唔會影響肉味<br />\n反而chill肉運到過黎仲大風險會off<br />\n其次 有其中一套講法就係煎一塊未解凍嘅扒<br />\n煎完再焗 佢嘅灰邊會細好多 同埋肉汁會多好多<br />\n仲有 roomtemp如果你煎med rare就注定失敗<br />\nmed都可能仲得"},{"pid":"d1121801f8669e0afba25e109e90b54b6854aa17","tid":312121,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/004303_29487734b8f2114561a13d7da2938ada.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F004303_29487734b8f2114561a13d7da2938ada.jpg&h=db89d828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾成熟真係好個人，靚牛不妨生d, 試下medium rare, 試過返唔到轉頭，熟晒起晒渣....我不如食其他</blockquote><br />\n睇落好有肥豬肉咁既感覺"},{"pid":"a3b903bdf2dcb488a00b283ebab558cd3a202a2c","tid":312121,"uid":4740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T19:29:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一黎太熟，二黎well done條邊太厚<br />\n<br />\n可能係<br />\n<br />\n太大火<br />\n聽人講只反一次先最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我雪櫃拎出黎室溫解涷一粒鐘到<br />\n大火起鑊兩分鐘<br />\n兩面煎一分鍾<br />\n邊位煎三十秒<br />\n最後再細火煎兩面分半鐘<br />\n<br />\n有邊d steps可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗解凍，睇料理的科學。有段片講解凍同點煎牛扒"},{"pid":"0a2c447c4df5d70583f7f682cca10f773a458b66","tid":312121,"uid":76511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T20:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冰鮮肉仲食7成？<br />\n<br />\n狗都唔屌</blockquote><br />\n閣下食新鮮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當日早上劏我覺得冇咩問題<br />\n<br />\n但冰鮮得起碼幾日<br />\n<br />\n一定要全熟<br />\n<br />\n同埋冰鮮得好食極有限</blockquote><br />\n隻牛死左超過一個鐘我已經唔會食。</blockquote><br />\n傻閪 平時係豬肉鋪買果d咪叫新鮮囉<br />\n<br />\n朝早劏完 就算放到夜晚先煮都好好味<br />\n<br />\n但一放落冰箱已經差好遠<br />\n<br />\n無論口感味道都好大分別</blockquote><br />\n你去香港啲最貴既扒房食下，問下啲牛係咪朝早劏囉，弱撚智</blockquote><br />\n一個鐘 笑死我 Aging 都唔知"},{"pid":"127525f82bdbb71330b4cba0c3d1366d300d95f6","tid":312121,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T01:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/184600_1575a554545ae5ba5003447fc9c1813c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F184600_1575a554545ae5ba5003447fc9c1813c.jpg&h=54dbc748&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/184603_5c00dc2c70abc3205d05ad2e332eeb4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F184603_5c00dc2c70abc3205d05ad2e332eeb4d.jpg&h=7e870745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢把斧點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好抵屌<br />\n$300唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抵喎？咁到食？300蚊就咁買扒都難"},{"pid":"2aed9a45ca24c22f5aa118a9321445cca9cecf9c","tid":312121,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>冰鮮肉仲食7成？<br />\n<br />\n狗都唔屌</blockquote><br />\n閣下食新鮮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當日早上劏我覺得冇咩問題<br />\n<br />\n但冰鮮得起碼幾日<br />\n<br />\n一定要全熟<br />\n<br />\n同埋冰鮮得好食極有限</blockquote><br />\n隻牛死左超過一個鐘我已經唔會食。</blockquote><br />\n傻閪 平時係豬肉鋪買果d咪叫新鮮囉<br />\n<br />\n朝早劏完 就算放到夜晚先煮都好好味<br />\n<br />\n但一放落冰箱已經差好遠<br />\n<br />\n無論口感味道都好大分別</blockquote><br />\n香港本地牛都唔啱做牛扒，大陸又嫌cheap，美國澳洲牛都要撘飛機過黎邊到會有新鮮牛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且有外國影片話啲牛就算新鮮都要放幾日雪櫃先好煮<br />\n<br />\n近年仲有啲熟成牛扒，敢問新鮮牛扒最好係師承何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4354e92f8094e653c1e8fbb868bdca07d60103e","tid":312121,"uid":45043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一黎太熟，二黎well done條邊太厚<br />\n<br />\n可能係<br />\n<br />\n太大火<br />\n聽人講只反一次先最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我雪櫃拎出黎室溫解涷一粒鐘到<br />\n大火起鑊兩分鐘<br />\n兩面煎一分鍾<br />\n邊位煎三十秒<br />\n最後再細火煎兩面分半鐘<br />\n<br />\n有邊d steps可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n7成唔係問題，但你well done 部份太厚，起晒渣，鞋過沙紙<br />\n最好買d厚野，1.5吋，再厚就要焗先靚<br />\n<br />\n下次試下大火半分鐘一面封面，之後細返d火（其實都仲係中大火）再煎，每一分鐘反一次，煎到去心目中想要度數<br />\n<br />\n塊野離左火，d熱仲係傳緊入個心，離左火個心起碼仲可以升多3度，如果你用溫度計，早幾度好離火，佢會繼續煮同收返d汁，唔好睇少果幾度，已經夠medium 變成medium well<br />\n<br />\n幾成熟係講個溫度，你要諗下點樣煎可以令到成舊野，由面到心都差唔多溫度，你太大火/好耐先反一次，表面會太高溫熟晒，但d熱又未傳到入心，到個心有7成熟時，well done 部分就會太厚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0424b40849fce1b1423959c1abb8c3b1baaf0f13","tid":312121,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"樓主愛食鞋底？"},{"pid":"bdda9e51dc5a5b584a893b9674f3b8f2195d1ac2","tid":312121,"uid":11428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/184600_1575a554545ae5ba5003447fc9c1813c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F184600_1575a554545ae5ba5003447fc9c1813c.jpg&h=54dbc748&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/184603_5c00dc2c70abc3205d05ad2e332eeb4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F184603_5c00dc2c70abc3205d05ad2e332eeb4d.jpg&h=7e870745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢把斧點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm